movies.title: Jillian Michaels: Kickbox Fastfix
movies.plot: Jillian Michaels Kickbox FastFix is a total body workout that will fix your physique fast!! These quick-paced workouts will blast off the fat while toning your entire body.
movies.simplePlot: Jillian Michaels Kickbox FastFix is a total body workout that will fix your physique fast!! These quick-paced workouts will blast off the fat while toning your entire body.

biography.bio: Jillian Michaels was born on February 18, 1974 in Los Angeles, California, USA. She is an actress and producer, known for The Biggest Loser (2004), Just Jillian (2016) and Jillian Michaels - 30 Day Shred (2008).
biography.name: Jillian Michaels
